      • export

        public void export(FeatureSet featureSet)
            throws ExporttoServiceException
        Description copied from interface: ExporttoService
        This method export a FeatureSet to other FeatureSet. The other necessary parameters to make this conversion are specific for every ExporttoService. e.g: a shape exporter needs a file and a projection, a database exporter needs a connection parameters...
        Specified by:
        export in interface ExporttoService
        Parameters:
        featureSet - the set of features hat have to be exported.
        Throws:
        ExporttoServiceException - if there is any exception in the exporting process
